### TEST 12: REGISTER MISSING FIELD

### ==========================================

POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
"name": "Incomplete User",
"email": "[incomplete@test.com](mailto:incomplete@test.com)"
}

### ==========================================

### TEST 13: DELETE USER WITHOUT TOKEN

### ==========================================

DELETE {{baseUrl}}/user/test-id

### ==========================================

### TEST 14: DELETE USER WITH TENANT TOKEN

### ==========================================

DELETE {{baseUrl}}/user/test-id
Authorization: Bearer {{loginTenant.response.body.data.access_token}}

